\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5663771\charrsid15100875 butcher}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9117970\charrsid15100875 , were they what they used to call block ends?
