Invariably on a Sunday, I - I was the favourite boy of my father, I don't mind saying that, and - come on Harry - get your things on, we'}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5663771\charrsid15100875 ll}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
