 the other end of - Garrett Lane to Tooting and back again, and invariably on those walks he'd pull up a milkman and they used to come round with cans then, milkmen had cans, hung - hung on a - a - an iron bar with a hook on the back there and - he'd ask 
for a - a ha'p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5663771\charrsid15100875 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9117970\charrsid15100875 rth of milk and we drank it out the can.
