g, make father and mother a cup of tea, and it was always me - until I - you know - the other youngster came along - and - yes, I always made them a cup of tea and took it up to their -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7894345 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9117970\charrsid15100875 You were the first one up were you?
