sed to put the alarm on for about six o'clock, perhaps father had to be at work at eight o'clock you see so I'd make them a cup of tea, mother'd get up and get his breakfast, get him off to work, then she'd see about us kids. We'd have porridge or - bread
 and milk or something like that you know.
