 in the morning 'til half past five at night, half past twelve on Saturdays. Fifty-four hours a week we used to do there. And - anyway I got this job at Price's, I started as a little boy there, I'd - as 
I got older I got a different job you see. And I stayed there until - I went through the - right through the sawmill, it was in the sawmill department, packing case making and - and sawyer - sawing you know, and I stayed at that job, I went right through 
