Well climbing up these ladders the blooming wind was blowing, it was a snowing, bowler hat and overcoat and I'm climbing up ladders and
 going along scaffolding - oh dear. Anyway I got the job. I suppose I was there - oh - well we came right the way down, almost to the front, there was quite a lot of us doing it, and - any - way that - that was the finish of the cleaning down the Portland
