e railway, he said. He said, I'll tell you where to go and who to see. Wet to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}London{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Bridge{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 and saw the boss of this - what was on the railway. How old are you? Eighteen. I was only seventeen at the time. All right, give you a job. Carriage cleaning, at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname State}}Victoria
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} station. Uniform of course, it was all green }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12456976\charrsid15100875 corduroy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
