d. Anyway he was all right there, the old - old German chef there, he - and - all he'd sing all day, Daisy, Daisy, what is the matter mit you. Oh - nearly drove me mad. Well I got plenty of grub there you see, plenty of drink. And always - he'd got - half
 a dozen packets of Woodbines laying about you know, w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3568087\charrsid15100875 he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9117970\charrsid15100875 n}{
